            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-bottom"> <span class="rtp-meta-cat">Categories: </span> <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/category/news-items/" title="View all posts in News Items" rel="tag">News Items</a>        <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/05/27/license-plate-readers-stir-controversy-in-california-as-the-nypd-prepares-to-use-drones/#respond" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on License Plate Readers Stir Controversy in California as the NYPD Prepares to Use Drones">Leave a comment</a></span><span class="post-tags"> Tags:  <span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/4th-amendment/" rel="tag">4th Amendment</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/bill-bratton/" rel="tag">Bill Bratton</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/dhs/" rel="tag">DHS</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/police-state/" rel="tag">Police State</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/shot-detectors/" rel="tag">shot detectors</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/surveillance-state/" rel="tag">Surveillance State</a></span></span>                <span class="post-tags">Comments: </span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/05/27/license-plate-readers-stir-controversy-in-california-as-the-nypd-prepares-to-use-drones/#comments">1</a> 
